dc_description_s: 1 map ; 40 x 49 cm|Relief shown pictorially.|Text in cartouche in upper right corner of map, "Nomenclaturae et positionis locorum huius tabulae testimonia, pete en Thesauro nostro geographico."|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637,1652-1684, and 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
